{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701900/extras/description_gif_1.gif?t=1717436005\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701900/extras/description_heading_0.png?t=1717436005\" /><br><br>Fill the boots of the Grave Gunner, an expert gunslinger, in this fast-paced arena shooter. <br>Face off against swarms of undead creatures in a dark, gothic graveyard, employing expressive movement to evade them and powerful handguns to slay them.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701900/extras/description_heading_1.png?t=1717436005\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Conquer thirteen waves of ever-increasing difficulty.<br></li><li>Disintegrate a cast of distinct monster types using satisfying and responsive weapons.<br></li><li>Express your FPS movement skills with techniques such as sliding, rocket jumping, and bunny hopping.<br></li><li>Absorb gems from slain monsters to regain your health and stay in the fight longer.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701900/extras/description_gif_2.gif?t=1717436005\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701900/extras/description_heading_2.png?t=1717436005\" /><br><br>While the basic mechanics are easy to pick up, great skill is required to master the intricacies of the movement and the quick aim to vanquish your enemies swiftly.<br>The early waves should be relatively easy for veteran FPS players, introducing the various enemy types that you will be encountering. The later waves, however, quickly ramp up in difficulty. Only the most elite gunslingers shall defeat the final, almost impossible waves.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset